      "content": "又重置使用限制，真有你的 Open AI Sam 还说每周用户每增加一百万就重置一次，直到达到一千万用户 Sam Altman (@sama) To celebrate 3 million weekly codex users, we are resetting usage limits. We will do this every million users up to 10 million. Happy building! — https://nitter.net/sama/status/2041658719839383945#m",
